p.span: The Winnacunnet High School community believes in educating the whole student by providing a flexible, engaging, and supportive atmosphere where learning is relevant and lifelong. Students are encouraged to work both collaboratively and independently to foster effective communication. We are committed to providing an education that promotes creativity, innovation, critical thinking, problem-solving skills, and responsible decision making. We believe this will enable our students to become active, contributing citizens of their communities.
Our commitment to these beliefs will help prepare all students to achieve their full potential.
